func convert(_ s: String, _ numRows: Int) -> String {
    if numRows == 1 {
        return s;
    }
    var zString = String.init();
    for i in 0..<numRows {
        var j = i;
        while j < s.count {
            if i == 0 || i == numRows-1 {
                zString.append(s[s.index(s.startIndex, offsetBy: j)]);
                j = j+2*(numRows-1);
            } else {
                zString.append(s[s.index(s.startIndex, offsetBy: j)]);
                j = j+2*(numRows-i-1);
                if j < s.count {
                    zString.append(s[s.index(s.startIndex, offsetBy: j)]);
                }
                j = j+2*i;
            }
        }
    }
    return zString;
}
